						<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 border border-purple-100/40 shadow-sm">
							<div class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl mb-3 lg:mb-4">🚨</div>
							<h3 class="font-inter font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm lg:text-base mb-2">Alerte en cas de danger</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-500 text-xs lg:text-sm leading-relaxed font-normal">Si tu es en danger immédiat, ECHO peut alerter les personnes compétentes pour te protéger.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			{# CTA FINAL #}
			<section class="bg-[linear-gradient(to_bottom,rgba(204,175,231,0.39),rgba(204,175,231,0.39)),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#F0EEFF,#F1EAFA)] py-16 px-6 md:py-24 md:px-8 text-center" aria-labelledby="cta-title">
				<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center">
					<div class="mb-6 md:mb-8" aria-hidden="true">
						<div class="relative w-40 h-40 sm:w-56 sm:h-56 md:w-72 md:h-72 lg:w-[440px] lg:h-[440px]">
							<img src="{{ asset('images/echo.png') }}" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-contain animate-float relative z-10"/>
						</div>
					</div>
					<h2 id="cta-title" class="font-inter font-bold text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[64px] text-[#4A157D] mb-4 lg:mb-6 tracking-tight leading-tight lg:leading-none max-w-5xl mx-auto">
